	@{" HISTORY            " Link "history"} some words from the past.


USAGE:
======

/rx amserv.amirx                   - Run as normal, with settings from config.

/rx amserv.amirx [NICK]            - Server will run with [NICK] as masternick,
                                     overriding the config.


if something goes wrong; type this and wait 5 secs or so:
/rx amserv.amirx halt              - Stop previous running script.

NB! You can Stop the script by writing QUIT to the server.

@endnode


